Basically the design question is wether we want this :

``` java
Mockito.framework().addListener((VerificationFailure) System.out::println);
Mockito.framework().addListener((VerificationSuccess) System.out::println);

interface Verification { verificationMode, wantedMethod, verificationData }
interface VerificationFailure extends Verification { failureCause }
interface VerificationFailureListener extends MockitoListener {
        void on(VerificationFailure arg);
}
interface VerificationSuccess extends Verification { }
interface VerificationSuccessListener extends MockitoListener {
        void on(VerificationSuccess arg);
}
```

Or 

``` java
Mockito.framework().addListener((Verification) System.out::println);

